 VideoLAN is a free MPEG, MPEG2, DVD and DivX software solution.
 .
 This is a GGI plugin for vlc, the VideoLAN Client.  To activate it, use
 the `--vout ggi' flag or select the `ggi' vout plugin from the preferences
